![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TGwf7yj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So I work at a tiny Swedish supplier to automotive industries. As I got lunch today at work, by the salad bar in the canteen, I noticed a guy looking very much like Keanu Reeves.

Chuckling about it as I sat down by my colleagues, “It must be fun looking like Keanu Reeves”, I said. 

And yeah, it was him. He’s apparently involved in a motorcycle company, which we supply. I was too star struck to get any real work for the rest of the day. I didn’t want to bother him (celebs should have their privacy), but others that worked with him said he was a super nice guy, really down to earth.

Still a bit shocked he showed up here of all places.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GrWFliT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[superapan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Travel Insurance to Visit Your Own Country</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/K7wYvys</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tVlZDXw.jpg?1" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/K7wYvys</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[jfoobar]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Damn</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kEoUzzU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UWOzi19.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kEoUzzU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rexonasmuggler]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Awesome Human Definitely Thinking Of Future Generations</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/1zjDQZG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t2t6l9v.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://mymodernmet.com/hikmet-kaya-reforestation-turkey/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/1zjDQZG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4cGGR5A</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KYpM8JY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4cGGR5A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[introvertextrovertmashup]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Drwmlew</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1bCNbVT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Drwmlew</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[omnifella]]></dc:creator>